<L>__{interior subash's house night}
<A>__{aloka and three women huddled beside a window, amrita half hidden behind them. we pan across a staircase to another window, through which we see a doorway. in the doorway, subash turns to smile a shy smile at amrita; he shrugs. past him now, we see hasari facing subash's father and three uncles, surly men with hair matted with mustard oil. the ghoshes are all seated on low chairs and stools. hasari is standing.}
